'''克莉絲汀·珍·巴倫絲基'''（{{lang-en|Christine Jane Baranski}}，{{bd|1952年|5月2日}}），美國電視劇與舞台劇女演員，曾獲得一座[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]與兩座[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]。其演出作品有《[[「法」妻|「法」妻]]》（''The Good Wife''）、《[[生活大爆炸|生活大爆炸]]》（''The Big Bang Theory''）等。

克莉絲汀於1974年出道，並於1980年演出其首部[[百老匯|百老匯]]劇《捉迷藏》（''Hide and Seek''），其後並以《真相》（''The Real Thing''，1984）、《謠言》（''Rumors''，1989）先後拿下[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]最佳戲劇女主角。曾經演出過的[[百老匯|百老匯]]劇還有有《喧囂粗俗》（''Hurlyburly''，1984）、《藍葉之屋》（''The House of Blue Leaves''，1986）與《波音波音》（''Boeing-Boeing''，2008）等。

== 簡歷 ==
巴倫絲基出生於[[纽约州|纽约州]][[水牛城|水牛城]]，是維吉尼亞（舊姓馬茲洛斯基）與一家[[波兰语|波兰语]]報紙的編輯魯西恩·巴倫斯基的女兒<ref>[http://au.movies.yahoo.com/Christine+Baranski/biography/62265/family/ "Christine Baranski – Family and Companions – Yahoo!7 Movies"] {{Wayback|url=http://au.movies.yahoo.com/Christine+Baranski/biography/62265/family/ |date=20070314043533 }} movies.yahoo.com</ref><ref name=biofilm>[http://www.filmreference.com/film/60/Christine-Baranski.html "Christine Baranski Biography (1952–)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/60/Christine-Baranski.html |date=20201113074039 }} filmreference.com, accessed April 29, 2011</ref>。她是{{tsl|en|Polish Americans|波蘭裔美國人|波蘭裔}}美國人，祖父母是一家波蘭劇院的演員<ref>[http://www.wned.org/Productions/Polonia/default.asp "Western New York Public Broadcasting Association"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wned.org/Productions/Polonia/default.asp |date=20090105182937 }} wned.org</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Triplett | first = William | date = May 12, 2002 | title = For Baranski, A Most Meaty Opportunity; In 'Sweeney Todd,' Actress Sinks Her Teeth Into a Singing Role | work = The Washington Post | publisher = HighBeam Research | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-353138.html | access-date = 2016-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106102221/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-353138.html | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。巴倫斯基高中就讀水牛城郊區[[奇克托瓦加|奇克托瓦加]]的{{tsl|en|Villa Maria Motherhouse Complex|維拉瑪麗亞學院}}<ref>{{cite web | last = Rousuck | first = J. Wynn | title = The lady has it: Christine Baranski stars in 'Mame' for the 2nd time | url = http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2006-05-21/news/0605230411_1_mame-cybill-tony-award | work = [[The_Baltimore_Sun|The Baltimore Sun]] | date = May 21, 2006 | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archive-date = 2013-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130928003904/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2006-05-21/news/0605230411_1_mame-cybill-tony-award | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Gans 2006">{{cite web | last = Gans | first = Andrew | url = http://www.playbill.com/news/article/100312.html | title = DIVA TALK: Chatting with Mame's Christine Baranski | work = [[Playbill|Playbill]].com | date = June 16, 2006 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080829200526/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/100312.html | archivedate = 2008年8月29日 | accessdate = 2016年10月25日 }}</ref>。之後前往紐約的[[朱利亞德學院|朱利亞德學院]]就讀<ref>{{cite news | last = Shulman | first = Randy | date = June 8, 2006 | title = Christine Baranski: TV and stage actress talks about starring in 'Mame' and 'Cybill' | work = MetroWeekly.com | url = http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=2163 | accessdate = 2016-10-25 | archive-date = 2006-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060615200139/http://www.metroweekly.com/feature/?ak=2163 | dead-url = no }}</ref> (Drama Division ''Group 3'': 1970–1974)<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.juilliard.edu/alumni/news/news_decades/2009-2010/0909/index.php | title = Alumni News | publisher = [[The_Juilliard_School|The Juilliard School]] | date = September 2009 | accessdate = April 7, 2012 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120319/http://www.juilliard.edu/alumni/news/news_decades/2009-2010/0909/index.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>，1974年畢業，並取得[[文學士|文學士]]學位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://movies.nytimes.com/person/3796/Christine-Baranski/biography | title = Christine Baranski | work = All Movie Guide | publisher = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | accessdate = April 7, 2012 | archive-date = 2013-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130928193327/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/3796/Christine-Baranski/biography | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
巴倫絲基在1983年10月嫁給演員[[马特奥·考维斯|馬修·考爾斯]]，兩人婚姻持續到2014年5月22日考爾斯去世為止<ref name=biofilm/><ref>Simonson, Robert. [http://www.playbill.com/news/article/191551-Matthew-Cowles-Actor-and-Husband-of-Christine-Baranski-Dies "Matthew Cowles, Actor and Husband of Christine Baranski, Dies"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/191551-Matthew-Cowles-Actor-and-Husband-of-Christine-Baranski-Dies |date=20140527211652 }} playbill.com, May 27, 2014</ref>。夫妻倆生有兩個女兒，伊莎貝爾（1984年生）與莉莉（1987年生）<ref>{{cite news | last = Klein | first = Alvin | date = January 25, 1998 | title = THEATER; Being Irish And Being Married | work = The New York Times | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E06E0DD1F38F936A15752C0A96E958260 | accessdate = April 30, 2010}}</ref>。其中一人是執業律師，曾就讀法學院，並通過[[律師資格考試#美國|紐約律師考試]]，《[[「法」妻|「法」妻]]》播出期間，在[[布魯克林區|布魯克林區]]執業<ref>{{cite episode |title=Christine Baranski |series=The Late Show with Stephen Colbert |date=28 April 2016 |url=http://www.cbs.com/shows/the-late-show-with-stephen-colbert/video/GQXc9ojyK9I_tmNMSc_bj7_bWJMcJB_l/the-late-show-4-28-2016-julianna-margulies-christine-baranski-matt-czuchry-hank-azaria-phil-knight-/ |network=CBS |season=1 |number=131 |last=Colbert |first=Stephen (host) |access-date=2016-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011172829/http://www.cbs.com/shows/the-late-show-with-stephen-colbert/video/GQXc9ojyK9I_tmNMSc_bj7_bWJMcJB_l/the-late-show-4-28-2016-julianna-margulies-christine-baranski-matt-czuchry-hank-azaria-phil-knight-/ |archive-date=2016-10-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

